 "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Belleoffreedom", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "thelibertydaily.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBqfEaqe.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://thelibertydaily.com/leftist-billionaires-bankrolling-e-jean-carrolls-case-against/", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "POWERPLAY: Leftist Billionaire\u2019s Bankrolling E. Jean Carroll\u2019s Case Against Trump Draws Ethics Complaint", "last_comment_created": 1783902173714, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 3, "score_up": 44, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"description": "If you love the news, check out The Liberty Daily's homepage. (Daily Signal)\u2014The lawyer for E. Jean Carroll, the former magazine columnist who accused President Donald Trump of sexual assault, is facing scrutiny over outside funding of the case by a left-leaning billionaire. The National Legal and Policy Center, a watchdog group, filed a bar [\u2026]", "large_image": "zbSo0zEpYAxTeTEn.png", "title": "Leftist Billionaire\u2019s Bankrolling E. Jean Carroll\u2019s Case Against Trump Draws Ethics Complaint - \ud83d\udd14 The Liberty Daily"}, "post_flair_text": "\ud83d\udea8\u00a0\u00a0LOCK THEM UP\u00a0\u00a0\ud83d\udea8", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBqgL3tW", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 20, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8726016, "raw_content": "", "author": "majorwetod", "created": 1783913945238, "profile_picture": "x2ZM8s8zLm2o", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "CasuallyObservant", "is_video": true, "video_link": "https://cdn.videy.co/g7fWcr9Z1.mp4", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "cdn.videy.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://cdn.videy.co/g7fWcr9Z1.mp4", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Not today Satan!", "last_comment_created": 1783917309982, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 1, "score_up": 20, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ATBqgL4A2", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 17, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "censored", "id": 8726056, "raw_content": "A microscopic demographic- Black males aged 14-35, a mere 2.7% of the U.S. population \u2014 perpetrates approximately 40% of all homicides. Blacks as a whole (~13-14% of population) commit 50-55% of known murders, dominate gun homicides, and rack up wildly disproportionate shares of robberies (~50-60%), aggravated assaults, carjackings, and property crimes per long-running FBI and BJS data. This isn\u2019t \u201cpoverty\u201d or \u201clegacy of slavery.\u201d It\u2019s a persistent pattern of elevated violent criminality that turns cities into no-go zones, inflates national \u201cgun violence\u201d stats used as weapons to disarm law-abiding citizens, and erodes the social fabric for everyone else.\r\nThe 2022 Kia boys plague \u2014 packs of Black teens turning easy-to-steal cars into instruments of mayhem and viral clout \u2014 exposed the rot. Overwhelmed departments, terrified of \u201cracism\u201d accusations, flooded streets with Flock cameras instead of confronting the source. What started as a containment tool metastasized into an 80k-90k+ camera panopticon spanning 5,000+ communities, vacuuming billions of vehicle scans, building searchable life histories without warrants. Blue light surveillance towers, birthed in Black hellholes to babysit chaos, now infest suburbs and highways \u2014 blinking sentinels of a nation that surrendered.\r\nGovernment, media, and elites enforce doublethink: the statistics exist, the bodies pile up, but uttering the racial truth brands you thoughtcriminal. Fear of the \u201cracist\u201d label paralyzes policy, censors data, and protects the dysfunction \u2014 70%+ Black children born out of wedlock, cultures celebrating thugs, cognitive gaps unaddressed. Denial breeds explosion: more Black crime, more excuses, more surveillance. Privacy? Dead. Rights? Negotiable for safety. The Ministry of Truth calls it \u201cequity.\u201d Reality calls it the soft totalitarianism required to manage a demographic that refuses to assimilate to civilized norms.\r\nThe law-abiding majority pays the bill \u2014 stripped of privacy, firearms, mobility, and peace so the system can monitor and contain the endless Black-generated disorder. Flock, blue lights, data networks: this is the boot stamping on the human face, forever, because facing group reality was too \u201cmean.\u201d The grid tightens. Dissent is monitored. Freedom dissolves in the name of order the guilty refuse to provide. Data doesn\u2019t lie. The ruin is demographic. The authoritarian endgame is inevitable simply because of the fear of being called \u201cracist\u201d.", "author": "Fakename", "created": 1783917073398, "profile_picture": "snlsZ8OXpbCY", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Fakename", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "The Black Crime Tsunami Forcing Orwellian Techno-Tyranny on America.", "last_comment_created": 1783922311407, "content": "<p>A microscopic demographic- Black males aged 14-35, a mere 2.7% of the U.S. population \u2014 perpetrates approximately 40% of all homicides. Blacks as a whole (~13-14% of population) commit 50-55% of known murders, dominate gun homicides, and rack up wildly disproportionate shares of robberies (~50-60%), aggravated assaults, carjackings, and property crimes per long-running FBI and BJS data. This isn\u2019t \u201cpoverty\u201d or \u201clegacy of slavery.\u201d It\u2019s a persistent pattern of elevated violent criminality that turns cities into no-go zones, inflates national \u201cgun violence\u201d stats used as weapons to disarm law-abiding citizens, and erodes the social fabric for everyone else.\nThe 2022 Kia boys plague \u2014 packs of Black teens turning easy-to-steal cars into instruments of mayhem and viral clout \u2014 exposed the rot. Overwhelmed departments, terrified of \u201cracism\u201d accusations, flooded streets with Flock cameras instead of confronting the source. What started as a containment tool metastasized into an 80k-90k+ camera panopticon spanning 5,000+ communities, vacuuming billions of vehicle scans, building searchable life histories without warrants. Blue light surveillance towers, birthed in Black hellholes to babysit chaos, now infest suburbs and highways \u2014 blinking sentinels of a nation that surrendered.\nGovernment, media, and elites enforce doublethink: the statistics exist, the bodies pile up, but uttering the racial truth brands you thoughtcriminal. Fear of the \u201cracist\u201d label paralyzes policy, censors data, and protects the dysfunction \u2014 70%+ Black children born out of wedlock, cultures celebrating thugs, cognitive gaps unaddressed. Denial breeds explosion: more Black crime, more excuses, more surveillance. Privacy? Dead. Rights? Negotiable for safety. The Ministry of Truth calls it \u201cequity.\u201d Reality calls it the soft totalitarianism required to manage a demographic that refuses to assimilate to civilized norms.\nThe law-abiding majority pays the bill \u2014 stripped of privacy, firearms, mobility, and peace so the system can monitor and contain the endless Black-generated disorder. Flock, blue lights, data networks: this is the boot stamping on the human face, forever, because facing group reality was too \u201cmean.\u201d The grid tightens. Dissent is monitored. Freedom dissolves in the name of order the guilty refuse to provide. Data doesn\u2019t lie. The ruin is demographic. The authoritarian endgame is inevitable simply because of the fear of being called \u201cracist\u201d.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 4, "score_up": 17, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "\ud83d\udeab\u00a0\u00a01984\u00a0\u00a0\ud83d\udeab", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBqfDm2J", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 76, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8725487, "raw_content": "", "author": "Trick", "created": 1783887678796, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "imnotdeadyet", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.patriots.win", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBqfDm2J.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.patriots.win/post/RYPPKeO2gqpQ.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/8CYttAqV4XWTRA09.png", "width": 520, "content-type": "png", "height": 497